title: 90: The Target Haul Episode (February Edition)
itunes:title: The Target Haul Episode (February Edition)
description: In this episode, Lisa, Mikey, and Jamie are taste-testing a ton of HEALTHY food finds from Target: salsa, sauces, soups, frozen meals, tortillas, jerky, and MORE! Plus, the gang try Lean Pockets and Pop-Tarts, both wrapped in PRETZEL. AHHHH!!! This episode will have you running to Target, so make sure you head on over to our Foodcast page for a full list of the products we tried!
itunes:summary: We hit the bullseye with another great HAUL from Target!
